layout.house_prompt: A photography studio with a shooting area, an editing room, a client lounge, a dressing room, a props storage, an office, and a bathroom. The shooting area has two studio lights and a backdrop. The editing room has a desk with two monitors and a chair. The client lounge has a sofa and a coffee table. The dressing room has a vanity with a mirror on top and a clothing rack. The props storage has shelves with props including hats and bags. The office has a desk with a chair and a filing cabinet. The bathroom has a toilet and a sink.

shooting_area.text_description: A modern industrial photography shooting area with two studio lights and a backdrop; clean open floor with ample clearance for equipment.

client_lounge.text_description: A modern industrial client lounge with a sofa and a coffee table; welcoming waiting area near the entrance.

editing_room.text_description: A modern industrial editing room with a desk holding two monitors and a chair; focused workspace.

dressing_room.text_description: A modern industrial dressing room with a vanity with a mirror on top and a clothing rack; private prep space.

props_storage.text_description: A modern industrial props storage room with shelves holding props including hats and bags; organized storage.

office.text_description: A modern industrial office with a desk with a chair and a filing cabinet; admin workspace.

bathroom.text_description: A modern industrial bathroom with a toilet and a sink; simple and clean.
